} 9. f4 $146 {A new idea. So far, White has been very successful after 9.Be2.}
g6 10. Nd2 Be7 11. Nf3 Nxd3 {Black's reaction was very precise. Now White has
a choice.} 12. Qxd3 (12. cxd3 $5 {might lead to an interesting fight.}) 12...
c5 13. Rad1 d4 14. Bf2 Bf5 15. Qd2 O-O {and Black equalized comfortably in
